## Detailed info about the error and fix

* COMMAND
```sh
gulp install
```

* ERROR
```sh
inq.prompt(...).then is not a function
```

* CAUSE
```javascript
// package-lock.json
{
   // ....
    "inquirer": { "version": "0.10.1" … }
   // ....
}
```

* SOLUTION
```javascript
// package-lock.json
{
   // ....
    "inquirer": { "version": "3.2.x" … } // as indicated by prompt-sui@3.2.1
   // ....
}
